text: Kadyrovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kadyrovsky Selsoviet, Ilishevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 754 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Verkhneyarkeyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ilishevsky District
title: Kadyrovo, Ilishevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
